# Disk Management
    - Partitions
    - MBR
    - GPT
    - Mount Points
    - fdisk

# Partition:
    - Disk can be divide into parts called PARTITION
    - patrtitions allow you to Separate Data

# MBR  - Master Boot Record
    - Can only address 2TB disk space
    - 4 primary partitions

# GPT:
    - support upto 128 partitions
    - support upto 9.4 ZB disk size

# fdisk
    - alternate: gdisk, parted

# df command
    :: disk free command